          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为国求良将，来此太行山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘸嚧嘸嚧哎哟哟，你看太行山上火炮连天，倒也有些威风有些杀气，不免转去"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢。吓，大丈夫只有向前，哪有退后之理？还要上前通报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，门上哪位？"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报与你家千岁知道：有一故友要见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：外面有一故友要见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，千岁的故友甚多，叫他通上花名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面汉子听着：我家千岁故友甚多，叫你通上花名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你只说二龙山王英求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：二龙山上王英求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，既是王贤弟到了，大开寨门迎接。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王贤弟在在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚三哥在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英 （同笑） 哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁在上，小弟有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄也有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚、王英同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭贺三哥登龙位，一来叩贺二问安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。自从分别金沙滩，今日相逢太行山。贤弟请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃三哥升帐之所，小弟焉敢坐下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说，岂有不坐之礼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此告坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知贤弟驾到，愚兄未曾出寨远迎，多有得罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟轻造宝寨，望乞海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢，请坐。贤弟，自从金沙滩一别，贤弟一向何处安身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟与三哥在金沙滩别后，无处安身，带了一哨人马，逃到二龙山，做了几年"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英 （同笑） 呵哈呵哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，此乃武将后路，不足为奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说哪里话？愚兄备得酒宴，与贤弟畅饮几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟来得卤莽，怎好打扰？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰们，"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒宴可曾齐备？"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐备多时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将摆开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "太行山摆酒宴满心欢喜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄把盏尊贤弟细听详情："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到今日相逢在太行山前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，愚兄好有一比。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初金沙滩分别之后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好比何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好比那绣球花落江心难得相逢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声喽啰们满斟刘伶，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与贤弟放开怀满饮数杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有王英在太行宽心饮宴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢了姚三哥酒席厚情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待小弟与三哥细说根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天下惶惶刀兵动，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四海干戈不得太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你这里坐山寨全然不晓"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，饮酒就饮酒，不要管别人的闲事。纵反反不到太行山，纵杀杀不过俺姚"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刚。不要犯了为兄的将令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这里未开口把话封了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要扶汉只恐怕难上见难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无此人去归汉难保华夷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大丈夫酒醉英雄胆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕死怎得显威名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚三哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小主爷现在那邓州城内"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天下惶惶刀兵动，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四海干戈不太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "西北营中弟找兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "马蹄踹破锦江城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "汉刘失落锦乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "东华门杀得父寻子"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人头杀得如瓜滚"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘唐他把江山卖"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住口！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东华门杀得父寻子"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人头杀得如瓜滚"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘唐他把江山卖"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有王英在太行犯了一次令，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不把姚刚放在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一捆四十不顺情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫喽啰与我扯下去"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喽啰拖王英同下，内打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰 （内同白） 一五、一十，十五、二十，二五、三十，三五、四十。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喽啰扶王英同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺王英犯了什么罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四十军棍不容情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且看姚刚怎样行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挨步站在二堂上"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声贤弟你休怪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休怪为兄下绝情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾不记金沙滩头把誓盟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冤报冤来仇报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与贤弟赔个情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫喽啰与我斟上葡萄酒"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只说姚刚是个无情汉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却原来是个有义人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英降汉铁石心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行不得来也要行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚三哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咬定牙根坐了罢"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫酒饮腹内事在心"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜盈满脸来陪笑"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟言来你且听："
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四海干戈不太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉刘王失了锦绣乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下惶惶刀兵动"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘唐他把江山卖"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下惶惶刀兵动"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘唐他把江山卖"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小王英犯了二次令，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恼得姚刚怒气冲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八十军棍不徇情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声喽啰扯下去"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喽啰拖王英同下，内打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰 （内同白） 一五、一十，十五、二十，二五、三十，三五、四十。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喽啰扶王英同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒是我王英来差了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八十军棍实难挨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂声匹夫不是人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱步来在二堂上"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王将军算不得什么好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又听得两旁喽啰取笑我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑我王英不是好汉人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰！"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站稳了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双手撒开千斤力，两边喽啰倒尘埃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好汉好汉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好汉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄？"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咬定牙根朝上坐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看软座！"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂声匹夫你且听："
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霸占山寨逞英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钢刀出鞘也要行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贪生怕死岂是人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要你下山佐乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕你姚刚逞威风！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你把我怎样行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚三哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若不保汉刘主，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫你山寨一扫空。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住口！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小王英说话胆包天，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不把俺姚刚放心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辕门斩首不容宽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声喽啰将他忙上绑"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：钢刀虽快，不斩自来之人。千岁还要三思而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，倒是喽啰说得有理。哦，有了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰们、喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与我用麻绳一条，将王英绑在后营，日间打到晚，晚间打到天明。哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天堂有路你不去，地狱无门闯进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常言道耕牛老了遭鞭打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英犯令受此刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见喽啰两泪淋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫还要三思行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手搭凉棚往下看"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某家且退后帐内"
        },
        {
          "character": "喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
